# Fleet: the repo-local kubeconfig — the primary cluster-isolation guarantee. kind writes the
# loopkit cluster's credentials ONLY here (KUBECONFIG points at it), so ~/.kube/config is never
# touched, merged, or put at risk. Never commit it.
.kube/
